sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant P as getjetstream.app (web page)
    participant CS as Auth Content Script
    participant SW as Extension Service Worker
    participant API as Jetstream Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    rect rgb(243, 232, 253)
    Note over U,DB: Sign in to the Jetstream ACCOUNT (not Salesforce)
    U->>P: Sign in on getjetstream.app/web-extension/*
    P->>API: Standard Jetstream login + 2FA (see Web App auth)
    API->>DB: Verify user, check "chromeExtension" entitlement
    API->>API: POST /web-extension/auth/session -> issue JWT (encrypted at rest)
    API-->>P: Return Jetstream JWT
    end

    rect rgb(230, 244, 234)
    Note over P,SW: Bridge the token into the extension (content script injected on getjetstream.app only)
    P->>CS: window.postMessage TOKEN_EXCHANGE (JWT) [origin-checked]
    CS->>SW: browser.runtime.sendMessage TOKEN_EXCHANGE (JWT)
    SW->>SW: Store JWT in browser.storage.sync
    end

    rect rgb(252, 232, 230)
    Note over SW,DB: Periodic entitlement / auth re-verification
    SW->>API: POST /web-extension/auth/verify (JWT + X-EXT-DEVICE-ID + app version)
    API->>DB: Validate token + entitlement + device
    API-->>SW: OK (or 401 -> require re-login)
    end

    Note over SW,API: This flow authorizes the Jetstream account only.<br/>Salesforce access uses the live Salesforce session cookie (see SF data flow).
